snippet.title: Trucking 3D
snippet.description:
Download now from here!
 - http://bit.ly/29hwgaN

Check our website for this and more exciting games for Windows: http://gametroopers.net

Trucking 3D is the next simulation game from Game Troopers. In this game you drive all kind of trucks and transport construction materials.

Embark on a mission to construct different buildings and drive around in a variety of vehicles, from rusty old pick up trucks to shiny new American 18 Wheelers. Enjoy the colorful and cartoonish graphics and maneuver your truck in a lively 3D environment while completing your missions.
